    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>I would like to commend Roger Rosenblatt for his comments on Bret Easton Ellis's latest attempt at fiction. Of course, I'm being unfair to Mr. Ellis here because I haven't read "American Psycho," and don't plan to any time soon. I'm still trying to forget "Less Than Zero." JOHN P. MCLEAN Amherst, N.Y.</p>
      </block>
